<br>
My Epic has saved my ass more times then I can count. Many times on raids where I see wizards without an Epic fall to AE damage or get a second of agro, where my Epic Skin was just enough to let me survive. Currently my guild is raiding HoT 2-3 times a week, and those AE's SUCK!! My Epic's SKin is a nice buffer in there. <br>
<br>
The +10 mana regen would be great to solo with, but umm... well WTF is a level 60 gonna go off an solo? Come raid time we attack at FM on an Uber Mob and most of the time its very dead before I hit OOM as it is. I really can not think of a moment where getting +10 mana a tick is more important then 800 free hp's of agro. Fact is a dead wizard at 60% mana is still a DEAD WIZARD. I'd rather be at 20% medding then waitin on the ol' click stick.<br>
<br>
My vote.. NFW!!<br>
